#: C/mousetweaks.xml:408(title)
msgid "Description Of The Functions"
msgstr "功能描述"

#: C/mousetweaks.xml:410(para)
msgid ""
"The <application>Mousetweaks</application> application offers three new "
"pointer features to the user. These are: <placeholder-1/>"
msgstr ""
"<application>鼠标优化</application>程序为用户提供了三种新特性。"
"它们是:<placeholder-1/>"

#: C/mousetweaks.xml:427(title)
msgid "Simulated Secondary Click Description"
msgstr "二次点击模拟描述"

#: C/mousetweaks.xml:429(para)
msgid ""
"When the user activates this feature, he will be able to perform secondary "
"clicks by using the <mousebutton>primary mouse button</mousebutton>. This is "
"especially useful for users that have only one <mousebutton>mouse button</"
"mousebutton> at their disposal."
msgstr ""
"当用户激活这个特性时，他将可以通过用<mousebutton>首次鼠标按键</mousebutton>"
"来进行二次点击操作。这对那些手中的鼠标仅有一个<mousebutton>鼠标按键"
"</mousebutton>的用户尤其有用。"

#: C/mousetweaks.xml:435(title)
msgid "How Does It Work?"
msgstr "它如何运作？"

#: C/mousetweaks.xml:437(para)
msgid ""
"When this feature is enabled, mousetweaks performs a secondary click at the "
"location of the pointer, if the user keeps the <mousebutton>primary mouse "
"button</mousebutton> pressed without moving the pointer for a determined "
"time."
msgstr ""
"当开启这一特性时，鼠标优化程序在指针当前位置上进行一个二次点击，只要用户"
"在一个设定好的时间内保持鼠标不动，且一直按着<mousebutton>首次鼠标按键"
"</mousebutton>。"

#: C/mousetweaks.xml:442(para)
msgid ""
"How long the user has to hold the <mousebutton>primary mouse button</"
"mousebutton> pressed is determined by the delay slider under the activation "
"checkbox:"
msgstr ""
"用户所要按下<mousebutton>首次鼠标按键</mousebutton>的时间由鼠标活性复选"
"框中的延时滑动条决定:"

#: C/mousetweaks.xml:452(para)
msgid ""
"Picture showing the slider to set how long to hold the primary button for "
"the secondary click to be triggered"
msgstr ""
"图例显示的是设定需要按住首次按键多久才触发二次点击的滑动条"

#: C/mousetweaks.xml:459(title)
msgid "Differences To The Normal Secondary Click"
msgstr "与普通二次点击的差异"

#: C/mousetweaks.xml:461(para)
msgid ""
"As the simulated secondary click is not able to discard the "
"<mousebutton>mouse button down</mousebutton> gesture from the <mousebutton> "
"primary button press</mousebutton> of the user, it issues a primary click "
"before issuing the secondary click. In other words, each secondary click "
"performed by this function is immediately preceded by a primary click, and "
"this makes it behave a bit differently to the normal secondary click "
"performed by the <mousebutton>secondary mouse button</mousebutton>. For "
"example:"
msgstr ""
"由于二次点击模拟无法从用户<mousebutton>首次按下按键</mousebutton>中分出"
"<mousebutton>按下鼠标按键</mousebutton>动作，因此它将在发出二次点击前"
"发出一个首次点击信号。换句话说，此功能做出的每个二次点击都立即先做一个"
"首次点击，这样它就跟一个通过<mousebutton>二次鼠标点击按键</mousebutton>"
"进行的普通二次点击有所不同了。例如:"

#: C/mousetweaks.xml:472(para)
msgid ""
"It is not possible to perform a secondary click on multiple items because "
"the primary click issued before the secondary click deselects the items."
msgstr ""
"不可能在多个条目上进行二次点击，因为先于二次点击发出首次点击取消了那些条目。"

#: C/mousetweaks.xml:478(para)
msgid ""
"When the simulated secondary click is performed on the trash icon on the "
"panel, not only does the contextual menu appear, but the trash folder does "
"also open. (The former is caused by the secondary click, the latter by the "
"primary click preceding the right click.)"
msgstr ""
"当在面板回收站上进行二次点击模拟操作时，不仅会出来菜单文本，而且回收站"
"目录也会打开。(前者是由二次点击引起的，后者能先于右击的首次点击引起)"

#: C/mousetweaks.xml:487(para)
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"It is not possible to provide a list of all diverging behaviours, because it "
"depends on the reaction of the application receiving the secondary click "
"preceded by a primary click."
msgstr ""
"不可能提供所有分离行为列表，因为它依赖于收到先于二次点击的首次点击的程序"
"的反应。"

#: C/mousetweaks.xml:492(para)
msgid ""
"Some users may also be surprised by the consequences of the following: it is "
"not possible to perform a long motionless primary button click and hold, "
"without also triggering the secondary click. For example:"
msgstr ""
"某些用户也惊讶于如下结果:不可能进行长时间不移动的首次按键点击和按下，"
"同时还不触发一个二次点击操作。比如:"

#: C/mousetweaks.xml:499(para)
msgid ""
"When doing a motionless primary button click and hold on the arrow of a "
"scrollbar, the scrollbar jumps to the bottom after some time. This is in "
"fact the normal behaviour of a secondary click on an arrow of a scrollbar."
msgstr ""
"当进行不移动的首次按键点击并在一个滚动条的箭头上一直按着，一段时间后滚动"
"条跳到底部。事实上，这是在滚动条的箭头上进行二次点击的正常行为。"

#: C/mousetweaks.xml:505(para)
msgid ""
"To work around this behaviour, simply move the pointer immediately after "
"pressing the <mousebutton>primary mouse button</mousebutton>. This way the "
"simulated secondary click is not issued."
msgstr ""
"为避免这一行为，只要在按下<mousebutton>首次鼠标按键</mousebutton>后立即"
"轻移指针。这次不会发出二次点击模拟信号。"

#: C/mousetweaks.xml:516(title)
msgid "Dwell Click Description"
msgstr "增强型点击描述"

#: C/mousetweaks.xml:518(para)
msgid ""
"There are users that cannot use any hardware button. By activating the "
"<guilabel>Dwell Click</guilabel>, they can have the mouse perform the "
"various clicks without pressing any mouse button. The click types that can "
"be performed are: single primary click, double-click, drag click and "
"secondary click."
msgstr ""
"有的用户无法用任何物理按键。通过激活<guilable>增强型点击</guilable>，他们"
"能不按任何鼠标按键就进行各种点击操作。能进行的点击操作有:单独首次点击，"
"双击，拖拉点击还有二次点击。"

#: C/mousetweaks.xml:525(para)
msgid ""
"When the buttonless click is active, the <mousebutton>mouse buttons</"
"mousebutton> remain functional and it is still possible to click with the "
"<mousebutton>mouse buttons</mousebutton>."
msgstr ""
"当无需按键的点击形式被激活后，<mousebutton>鼠标按键</mousebuttons>还是"
"可用的，仍有可能用<mousebutton>鼠标按键</mousebutton>来进行点击操作。"

#: C/mousetweaks.xml:531(title)
msgid "Dwell Delay Setting"
msgstr "增强型延时设置"

#: C/mousetweaks.xml:533(para)
msgid ""
"With the <guilabel>Delay</guilabel> slider, the user can configure how long "
"the pointer has to be motionless for the click to be initiated."
msgstr ""
"通过<guilable>延时</guilable>滑动条，用户可以设置指针要静止多久才能"
"引发点击操作。"

#: C/mousetweaks.xml:543(para)
msgid "Picture showing the delay slider of the dwell click"
msgstr "图例显示的是增强型点击的延时滑动条"

#: C/mousetweaks.xml:547(para)
msgid ""
"Details about how to complete the click and how to choose the click type can "
"be found under <link linkend=\"mouse-a11y-dwell-modes\">How To Complete "
"Clicks And Specify The Click Type</link>."
msgstr ""
"有关如何完成点击操作以及如何选择点击方式的详细说明能在"
"<link linkend=\"mouse-a11y-dwell-modes\">如何完成点击并定义点击方式</link>"
"中找到。"

#: C/mousetweaks.xml:553(para)
msgid "The dwell delay only works in the context of the dwell click."
msgstr "增强型延时仅用于增强型点击模式中。"

#: C/mousetweaks.xml:559(title)
msgid "Motion Treshold Setting"
msgstr "移动阀值设置"

#: C/mousetweaks.xml:561(para)
msgid ""
"For people that have trouble to keep the mouse motionless, there is the "
"<guilabel>Motion Treshold</guilabel> slider."
msgstr ""
"对于那么保持鼠标绝对静止有困难的人来说，这里有个"
"<guilabel>移动阀值</guilabel>滑动条。"

#: C/mousetweaks.xml:570(para)
msgid "Picture showing the motion treshold slider of the dwell click"
msgstr "图例显示了增强型点击中的移动阀值滑动条"

#: C/mousetweaks.xml:575(para)
msgid ""
"When the slider is set towards low, even little mouse movements are "
"considered; however, by setting a higher treshold, the mouse has to traverse "
"a bigger distance before it is considered as moving."
msgstr ""
"当滑动条移向低位时，即使是小小的鼠标移动都会引发信号；而通过设一个较高的"
"阀值，鼠标就不得不移动一段较长的距离使计算机意识到鼠标移动了。"

#: C/mousetweaks.xml:581(para)
msgid "This function only works in the context of the dwell click."
msgstr "此功能仅在增强型点击中有效。"

#: C/mousetweaks.xml:587(title)
msgid "How To Complete Clicks And Specify The Click Type"
msgstr "如何完成点击并指定点击方式"

#: C/mousetweaks.xml:589(para)
msgid ""
"Each time she pointer stops moving, a click is initiated. How the click is "
"completed and how the click type is chosen depends on what dwell mode the "
"user has selected. The two available modes are:"
msgstr ""
"每当她(指针)停止移动时，就会引发一个点击操作。如何完成点击以及点击方式的"
"选择，它们都依赖于用户选择了哪种增强模式。有两种可用模式:"

#: C/mousetweaks.xml:600(para)
msgid "Picture showing the radio buttons to select dwell mode"
msgstr "图例显示了选择增强型模式的单选框"

#: C/mousetweaks.xml:605(para)
msgid ""
"To select the mode, the user only has to click on the radio button that "
"corresponds to his choice."
msgstr ""
"欲选此模式，用户仅需在他选的有关模式的单选框中点击。"

#: C/mousetweaks.xml:609(title)
msgid ""
"Dwell Click With Automatic Click Completion And Click Type Choice Beforehand"
msgstr ""
"带有自动点击完成和事先选择点击方式的增强型点击"

#: C/mousetweaks.xml:612(para)
msgid ""
"This mode is active when the user selects <guilabel>Choose type of click "
"beforehand</guilabel>. In fact, after the mouse has been motionless for the "
"time defined by the Delay slider, the system will automatically perform the "
"click type that is selected in the Click Type Window shown here:"
msgstr ""
"当用户选择<guilabel>事先选择点击方式</guilabel>的时候激活此模式。实际上，"
"在一段由延时滑动条指定的鼠标无移动时间后，系统会自动进行以下点击方式窗口中"
"显示出来的被选中的操作:"

#: C/mousetweaks.xml:624(para)
msgid "Picture showing the click type window"
msgstr "图例显示了点击方式窗口"

#: C/mousetweaks.xml:628(para)
msgid ""
"To display the click type window on the screen, the user has to put a "
"checkmark <application>in the checkbox named <quote>Show click type window</"
"quote>:</application>"
msgstr ""
"欲在屏幕上显示点击方式窗口，用户必须选中<application>名为<quote>显示点击方式"
"窗口</quote>的复选框</application>"

#: C/mousetweaks.xml:638(para)
msgid "Picture with the checkbox to display the click type window"
msgstr "带有复选框的图例显示了点击方式窗口"

#: C/mousetweaks.xml:643(para)
msgid ""
"After the click has occurred, the single click type will be automatically "
"restored. In order to choose another click type, the user has to perform an "
"automatic click on the <guibutton>button</guibutton> in the Click Type "
"Window that corresponds to its click type choice."
msgstr ""
"在点击操作发生后，单一点击方式将被自己还原。为选择另一点击方式，用户必须在"
"点击方式窗口中有关点击方式选择的<guibutton>按钮</guibutton>上进行自己点击。"

#: C/mousetweaks.xml:649(para)
msgid ""
"Some users might prefer to use the <guilabel>Dwell Click panel applet</"
"guilabel> instead of the Click Type Window. The advantage of the panel "
"applet is that it does not cover any open window on the desktop."
msgstr ""
"有些用户可能更愿意使用<guilabel>增强型点击面板小程序</guilabel>来代替"
"点击方式窗口。面板小程序的好处就是，它不会盖住桌面打开的任务窗口。"

#: C/mousetweaks.xml:660(para)
msgid "Picture showing the click type applet at the right of the gnome menus"
msgstr "图例显示了 gnome 菜单中的点击方式小程序"

#: C/mousetweaks.xml:665(para)
msgid ""
"To display the click type applet on the GNOME panel, please follow the "
"procedure you have to use in order to add any applet to the GNOME panel. If "
"you do not know how to add an applet to the panel, have a look at <link "
"linkend=\"mouse-a11y-start-pointer-capture\">Starting The Pointer Capture "
"Function</link>."
msgstr ""
"为在 GNOME 面板上显示点击方式小程序，请遵循您为添加其它小程序至 GNOME 面板"
"所采用的方式。如果您不知道如果将一个小程序添加至面板，请看 <link "
"linkend=\"mouse-a11y-start-pointer-capture\">开启指针锁定功能</link>。"


#: C/mousetweaks.xml:672(para)
msgid ""
"The click type window and the click type applet can be used simultaneously "
"or each on its own."
msgstr ""
"点击方式窗口和点击方式小程序能同时使用，或每次用一个。"

#: C/mousetweaks.xml:677(title)
msgid ""
"Dwell Click With Click Type Choice And Click Completion By A Mouse Gesture"
msgstr ""
"带有点击方式选择的增强型点击和通过鼠标手势完成点击"

#: C/mousetweaks.xml:680(para)
msgid ""
"This mode is active when the user selects <guilabel>Choose type of click "
"with mouse gestures</guilabel>. In fact, after the mouse has been motionless "
"for the above predefined delay, the shape of the pointer will change for a "
"little while:"
msgstr ""
"当用户选择<guilabel>选择带有鼠标手势的点击方式</guilabel>时会激活此模式。"
"实际上，在以上预定的鼠标无移动延时后，指针形状将有所改变:"

#: C/mousetweaks.xml:687(para)
msgid ""
"If the user moves the mouse while it is showing the alternative shape, a "
"click is performed and the pointer returns to its normal shape. The type of "
"click performed depends on the direction of the movement of the mouse."
msgstr ""
"如果用户在指针显示成另一形状时移动鼠标，这将进行点击操作并使指针回到原来的"
"形状。点击操作的方式依赖于鼠标移动的方向。"

#: C/mousetweaks.xml:694(para)
msgid ""
"If the user keeps the mouse motionless until the pointer returns to its "
"normal shape, the user can move the mouse without a click being performed. "
"The next dwell click can be performed when the mouse stops moving again."
msgstr ""
"如果用户直到指针变回原来形状还未移动过鼠标，那用户就能移动鼠标而不会发生"
"点击操作。当鼠标再次停止移动时才会触发下一个增强型点击。"

#: C/mousetweaks.xml:701(para)
msgid ""
"The user also has the possibility to match click type with movement "
"direction by using the 4 <guimenu>popups</guimenu> available under this mode:"
msgstr ""
"用户也有可能通过用此模式下可用的4个<guimenu>弹出菜单</guimenu>来匹配移动"
"方向:"

#: C/mousetweaks.xml:711(para)
msgid ""
"Picture showing the configuration options to map click type to movement "
"direction"
msgstr ""
"图例显示了有关移动方向的点击方式的配置选项"

#: C/mousetweaks.xml:716(para)
msgid ""
"There is also a <guimenuitem>Disabled</guimenuitem> menu item in each "
"<guimenu>popup</guimenu>. The user can select it if he does not want some "
"click types to be performed automatically. This is especially interesting "
"for users that have problems only with certain click types."
msgstr ""
"在每个<guimenu>弹出菜单</guimenu>中也有一个<guimenuitem>关闭</guimenuitem>"
"选项。如果用户不希望某些点击方式自动进行的话，他可以选择这一项。那些对于"
"特定点击方式成问题的用户尤其喜欢这个选项。"

#: C/mousetweaks.xml:726(title)
msgid "Locking The Pointer Description"
msgstr "锁住指针的描述"

#: C/mousetweaks.xml:728(para)
msgid ""
"There are people that have to use their pointing device not only for the "
"computer. These people would welcome a way to lock the pointer into an area "
"of the screen, so that they can use their pointing device for other tasks."
msgstr ""
"有些用户不仅仅是为用电脑而使用他们的鼠标设备，这些用户会需要一个将指针锁在"
"屏幕中某一区域的功能，这种他们就可以将鼠标用于其它操作。"

#: C/mousetweaks.xml:733(para)
msgid ""
"In fact, the Pointer Capture panel applet creates such an area on the panel, "
"into which the user can lock the pointer until he releases it in a "
"determined way."
msgstr ""
"实际上，指针锁定面板小程序在面板上创建了那么一块区域，用户能将指针锁在那里，"
"直到它用设定好的方式解除锁定。"

#: C/mousetweaks.xml:737(remark)
msgid ""
"Have a look at <placeholder-1/> for instructions about how to install the "
"pointer capture applet on the GNOME panel."
msgstr ""
"参看 <placeholder-1/> 如何在 GNOME 面板上引入指针锁定小程序的简介。"

#: C/mousetweaks.xml:757(para)
msgid "Picture of the pointer capture area when the pointer has been captured"
msgstr "指针被锁在指针锁定区域的图例"

#: C/mousetweaks.xml:762(para)
msgid ""
"By choosing Preferences in the contextual menu of the pointer capture "
"applet, the user gets a window with the options of the pointer capture "
"applet:"
msgstr ""
"通过选择指针锁定小程序的菜单文本中的选项，用户可获得指针锁定小程序的"
"选项窗口:"

#: C/mousetweaks.xml:772(para)
msgid "Picture showing the preferences of the pointer capture applet"
msgstr "图例显示了指针锁定小程序的选项"

#: C/mousetweaks.xml:777(para)
msgid ""
"The preferences window of the pointer capture applet has three sections:"
msgstr ""
"指针锁定小程序的选项窗口分为三部分:"

#: C/mousetweaks.xml:782(para)
msgid ""
"In the Capture Pointer section, the user can specify under what "
"circumstances the pointer gets captured when it moves into the capture area. "
"For example: if the control modifier is checked, the pointer gets captured "
"when it is over the capture area and the user presses the Control modifier "
"key. If no modifier is checked and the mouse button is set to 0, the pointer "
"only has to move into the capture area to get locked."
msgstr ""
"在指针锁定部分，用户可定义当指针移入锁定区域时，在什么情况下应该锁住指针。"
"比如:如果指针超出锁定区域并按下了定义的组合键 ctrl，就锁住指针。如果未"
"选中组合键并将鼠标按键设为 0，那只有当指针移入锁定区域时才被锁住。"

#: C/mousetweaks.xml:790(para) C/mousetweaks.xml:798(para)
msgid ""
"It is also possible to specify a combination of modifiers and mouse button."
msgstr ""
"这里也可以定义一系列的组合键和鼠标按键。"

#: C/mousetweaks.xml:795(para)
msgid ""
"In the Release Pointer section, the user can specify what modifier or mouse "
"button releases the pointer."
msgstr ""
"在释放指针部分，用户可定义用什么组合键或是鼠标按键来释放指针。"

#: C/mousetweaks.xml:803(para)
msgid ""
"In the Size of Capture Area section, the user can specify the width of the "
"capture area on the GNOME panel."
msgstr ""
"在锁定区域范围部分，用户能定义 GNOME 面板上锁定区域的宽度。"

